274
00:28:54,660 --> 00:29:00,150
There's more than one chest of value in these waters.

275
00:29:00,150 --> 00:29:04,650
So perhaps you may wish to enhance your offer.

276
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:11,620
Consider it in your calculations that you robbed me of my wedding night.

277
00:29:11,620 --> 00:29:13,350
So I did.

278
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:20,170
A marriage interrupted.

279
00:29:20,170 --> 00:29:23,660
Or fate intervenes.

280
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:26,850
You're making great efforts to ensure Jack Sparrow's freedom.

281
00:29:26,850 --> 00:29:28,070
These are not going to Jack.

282
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:32,870
Oh, really. To insure Mr. Turner's freedom?

283
00:29:32,870 --> 00:29:39,080
I'll still want that compass. Consider that in your calculations.

284
00:29:58,580 --> 00:30:01,740
Well, I say it was divine providence what escaped us from jail.

285
00:30:01,740 --> 00:30:08,540
And I'll say, it was me being clever. Ain't that right, poochy?

286
00:30:08,540 --> 00:30:12,640
Well, how d'you know it weren't divine providence what inspired you to be clever.

287
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:14,750
Anyways, I'm no' stealing no ship.

288
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:20,130
It ain't stealing, it's salvaging. And since when did you care?

289
00:30:20,130 --> 00:30:24,420
Since we're not immortal no more. We've got to take care of our immortal souls.

290
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:26,400
