307
00:32:34,340 --> 00:32:40,880
Worse, as it turns out. You see, the Pelegostos believe that Jack is a god in human form.

308
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:45,680
And they intend to do 'im the honor of releasing him from his fleshy prison.

309
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:54,100
They'll roast him and eat him.

310
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:56,080
