Put your legs through! Start the climb!

323
00:35:52,170 --> 00:35:56,430
Come on men, it'll take all of us to crew the Black Pearl!

324
00:35:56,430 --> 00:36:01,520
Actually, you wouldn't need everyone. About six would do.

325
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:09,850
Oooh, dear.

326
00:36:09,850 --> 00:36:12,010
Hurry!

327
00:36:16,030 --> 00:36:18,940
Heave! Is that all you've got?

328
00:36:26,970 --> 00:36:30,340
