Roll the cage!

338
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,290
Lift the cage!

339
00:38:59,290 --> 00:39:00,880
Hurry!

340
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:03,300
Lift it high like a lady's skirt.

341
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,160
This way lads.

342
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,710
Stop it!

343
00:42:04,820 --> 00:42:10,050
Pull loose the mooring line. The mooring line!

344
00:42:10,050 --> 00:42:14,490
Hey! Little hairy thing. Give it back!  Don't bite it!

345
00:42:14,490 --> 00:42:17,000
Pull loose the mooring line!

346
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:19,120
It's got me eye. It won't give it back.

347
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:20,770
Well, how'd you get it back last time?

348
00:42:20,770 --> 00:42:22,620
Excellent! Our work's half done!

349
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:25,450
We done it for you! Knew you'd be coming back for it.

350
00:42:25,450 --> 00:42:26,810
Make ready to sail, boys!

351
00:42:26,810 --> 00:42:29,930
What about Jack? I won't leave without him.

352
00:42:29,930 --> 00:42:31,350
Oi!

353
00:42:39,370 --> 00:42:40,830
Time to go.

354
00:42:40,830 --> 00:42:43,660
Cast off those lines!

355
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,550
Make ready to cast off!

356
00:42:57,750 --> 00:42:58,930
