490
00:54:35,980 --> 00:54:42,410
Land is where you will be safe, Jack Sparrow, and so you will carry land with you.

491
00:54:50,620 --> 00:54:55,640
Dirt. This is a jar of dirt.

492
00:54:55,640 --> 00:54:57,460
Yes.

493
00:55:00,390 --> 00:55:02,870
